  m_Name: Trial of Weaving 2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestDefinition
  QuestId: Trial of Weaving 2
  QuestTitle: Trial of Weaving 2
  QuestObjective: Cast 15 Spells
  QuestDescription: "The ICE agents patrol the city gates. You are instructed to
    stir the crowd\u2019s fear and anger, let unrest ripple through the market squares
    and alleyways, and fracture the authority that binds the people.\n\nEnsure that
    the city believes the turmoil rose from its own shadows, not from the hand that
    pays you."
  QuestOutcome: "There is a stillness after each incantation, as though the world
    itself pauses to listen.\n\nWhen the fifth spell leaves your lips, the silence
    lingers a moment too long\u2014heavy with quiet calculation."
  MaxProgress: 15
